data.eml:eml: New species of the subfamily Braconinae (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) from the Russian Far East

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Samartsev, Konstantin G. (2018): New species of the subfamily Braconinae (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) from the Russian Far East. Zootaxa 4388 (2): 238-254, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4388.2.6
